We understand that getting donors involved is not an easy task. That is why we launched an initiative to help increase awareness and make your fundraiser a success!

Every customer who signs up for a Donor Web Site will be eligible to sign up for the Bricks R Us Share Your Cause initiative.

Share Your Cause is a new service offered to our customers free of charge. The goal is to make your fundraiser a success by promoting your cause to a global audience. Through Share Your Cause, Bricks R Us will optimize your donor website and share your campaign throughout social media so you can reach more donors.
<h2>How It Works:</h2>
<ul>
	<li>You donor website will be optimized to engage more donors</li>
	<li>We will promote your <a href="http://www.bricksrus.com/services/donor-web-site/">Donor Website</a> through our various social media channels (i.e. Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, etc.)</li>
	<li>We will include a call to action on our social promotions to engage more donors</li>
</ul>
<h2>How This Benefits You:</h2>
<ul>
	<li>Your campaign will receive a global audience</li>
	<li>Your Donor Website will receive more views from prospective donors</li>
	<li>The service is FREE of charge!</li>
</ul>
Share Your Cause is a Bricks R Us initiative that is not offered by other engraved brick companies. Bricks R Us is more than just your local brick engraving company. Our team cares about our customers; that is why we are constantly looking for new, innovative ways to help your fundraiser become a success.

